name: Iceland volcano eruption
summary: Volcanic activity continues on Iceland's Reykjanes Peninsula, with the volcano erupting for the seventh time in the past year. The latest eruption has prompted evacuations, as lava and ash are spewing out. Travel advisories have been issued, and updates on the Blue Lagoon natural spa have been provided. The eruption is near Iceland's capital, and a passenger plane captured video of the event. Authorities have been closely monitoring the situation, and no disruptions have been reported. The volcano has now erupted ten times in the past three years, but despite the frequent eruptions, tourists remain fascinated, with one capturing the eruption from a plane window.

name: Captain Tom
summary: An investigation has uncovered mismanagement and personal benefits for the family of Captain Tom Moore, the war veteran who raised millions for charity. The report revealed that the Captain Tom Foundation, set up in Moore's name, was "not set up properly" and lacked financial controls. The family is accused of "repeatedly" benefiting from the charity, including receiving inflated salaries and fees. The inquiry also found that Moore's daughter, Hannah Ingram-Moore, kept £1.5 million from book sales and requested a £150,000 salary to run the charity. The revelations have shocked and embarrassed the community where Moore lived, tarnishing his legacy as a national hero.

Meanwhile, various outlets provide details about the funeral itself, including the attendance of other One Direction members and A-list celebrities. name: Ken Reid
summary: Ken Reid, a renowned Northern Irish journalist and former political editor of UTV, has passed away at the age of 69. Tributes have poured in from various organizations and individuals, including the Department of Health, BBC, The Irish News, and the Belfast Telegraph. Family and colleagues have expressed their sadness, and funeral details have been released. Ken Reid was widely respected for his contributions to journalism in Northern Ireland, having played a pivotal role in shaping public discourse and providing insights into complex political issues. His death has been met with an outpouring of grief and recognition, with many acknowledging his significant impact on the profession and on society as a whole.
